AppImage Type 2 Static Runtime — Third-Party Notices
=====================================================

The AppImage static type2-runtime bundled in Speedwave is a pre-built binary
from the AppImage/type2-runtime project. It serves as the AppImage header that
mounts the SquashFS payload (Speedwave application) without requiring libfuse2
on the host system.

Source: https://github.com/AppImage/type2-runtime

The runtime statically links the following libraries:

